title: [Gorget Trails, Foothills]
description: Quartz-veined boulders interrupt the green wash of tall grass and darker splotches of bushes.  A flock of parrots bursts out of the forest canopy to the southwest, circling madly, then plunges back into the rippling sea of leaves.
